name: GAIM Range
summary: GAIM Range, the ultimate VR home gun range simulator. Bring the thrill of a customized gun range directly to your fingertips. You have complete control. Set up steel and paper targets exactly where you desire, strategically position IPSC walls, and navigate through your own home while shooting. With precise ballistics and realistic firearms controllers, GAIM Range allows you to hone your skills, and develop muscle memory like never before.
